The '''Legion Condor EX''' was a [[Starship/Legends|starship]] model that was in use around the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was capable of [[Hyperspace/Legends|hyperspace]] travel and was popular with starship renters.

The process of renting one of these ships was similar, in many ways, as with renting others. The rentor could pay for a fixed number of hyperspace jumps upfront. Upon reaching the last jump, the ship would automatically return to base. However, if a rentor attempted to override this programming or jump-tamper the [[Navigation computer/Legends|nav-computer]], they would face a hefty fine or be ordered to a weekend flying school with a tough [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] instructor. There was also collision insurance and medical coverage available with the rental.

